room_title: Escape room "Escape the Haunted House" by Xcape Branson in Branson
room_address: 236 Wild Valley Way Branson West, MO 65737
room_description:
All you wanted was a peek of the old haunted mansion, and now you seriously regret it. The door has locked behind you, trapping you inside. And to make matters worse, legend has it that anyone who has stayed in the mansion longer than an hour has perished.
The floor starts to creak, ghosts float through the rooms, and somehow things are coming alive. Many hidden horrors await as you try to solve the puzzle of how to escape this Haunted House.
